org.apache.juneau.rest.client

Class DateHeader

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.http.message.BasicHeader
      • org.apache.juneau.rest.client.DateHeader
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Cloneable, org.apache.http.Header, org.apache.http.NameValuePair

    public final class DateHeader
extends org.apache.http.message.BasicHeader
    Convenience class for setting date headers in RFC2616 format.

    Equivalent to the following code:

    Header h = new Header(name, DateUtils.formatDate(value));

    See Also:
